{"body": "@spastorino while there are hardlinks and symlinks on Windows, Ruby doesn't know about them.\r\n\r\n`symlink` and `link` will raise `NotImplementedError` on Windows, so default to `:duplicate` seems fine with me (there will be no broken experience)\r\n\r\nIf user has the option to customize, and knows what he is doing with symlinks or hardlinks, then fine.\r\n\r\n", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/2024266", "created_at": "2011-09-07T00:53:47Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/2886#issuecomment-2024266", "updated_at": "2011-09-07T00:53:47Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 2886, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/luislavena/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/luislavena/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/luislavena/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/luislavena", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/luislavena/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/luislavena", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/luislavena/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/e7cff3cfd41c495e1012227d7dc24202?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F13e5ebb0fa112fe1b31a1067962d74a7.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/luislavena/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/luislavena/received_events", "gravatar_id": "e7cff3cfd41c495e1012227d7dc24202", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/luislavena/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "luislavena", "type": "User", "id": 4182, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/luislavena/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52383e0abd3543c15101052f"}, "id": 2024266, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/2886"}
